{"tid":2516095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 重有10日你d 私隱資料就會同facebook 共享","createTime":"2021-05-04T12:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T12:28:55.000Z","uid":344403,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e580dac5646b6d8eed4963b054b1d1dd88498a8","tid":2516095,"uid":344403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp在1月5日更新私隱條款，要求用戶同意將其個人數據與母公司facebook共享，否則帳戶會在限期後被移除。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp宣布將會推遲該新政策至<span class=\"red\">5月15日</span>推出，並強調有關更新只為增加平台上的商業交易，不會影響用戶間的個人通訊。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">拒絕暫緩！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉Signal 係勢在必行，<span class=\"red\">最後10日</span>，身邊重有朋友未轉既快d 叫佢轉/用方法引佢地轉啦<br />\nDownload link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://signal.org/download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=f6ca4cea\" target=\"_blank\">https://signal.org/download/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Q&amp;A</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n1.而家都未轉既人，都唔會係同路人？<br />\nA：現實就係好多怕麻煩 有種種理由唔轉住既人，但唔代表佢地無得救。行多一步，試下勸又好，幫佢解決d 麻煩 教佢點搵sticker都好，做多少少令佢地唔好怕試新事物。<br />\n<br />\n2.TG 重好用啦，點解用Signal?<br />\nA：好多post已經討論過所以呢邊唔討論，兩邊各有好處，唔洗斷曬自己選擇既路，揀自己鐘意果邊。<br />\n<br />\n3.Signal 重係好多問題，又lag 又成日收唔到msg?<br />\nA：我都係用家身同感受，但暫時同失去私隱黎講，我會接受等待，等Signal 慢慢改好，比起要放棄私隱，呢個係個人既堅持。可能因為Signal group chat 都有end-to-end encrypted，所以一多人send msg 就會好耐或者lag。 <br />\n<br />\n4.係公司無網頁版好唔方便？<br />\nA：想安全但又想方便，自然要拎個平衡。我唔知技術上做唔做到又安全，又有web版，但你有要求時，希望大家都要學識付出！我有donate支持Signal，希望佢越來越好，有能力既朋友都支持下啦！ 又或者幫d 懶到出汁還未轉Signal 既人, 鞏困用戶量，都會令Signal 改善得更快更好。<br />\n<a href=\"https://signal.org/donate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdonate%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=20542361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://signal.org/donate/</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n由Whatsapp 轉Signal 需要知道既msg backup, 同埋方便搵sticker 既方法<br />\n<br />\n1. Whatsapp 對話及facebook紀錄備份教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.metropop.com.hk/移民前做足準備-WhatsApp-Facebook-備份教學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metropop.com.hk%2F%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E5%81%9A%E8%B6%B3%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99-WhatsApp-Facebook-%E5%82%99%E4%BB%BD%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=2226ffe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.metropop.com.hk/移民前做足準備-WhatsApp-Facebook-備份教學</a><br />\n<br />\n上網都好多呢d 教學，google 搵下就有，share 俾d 怕麻煩既朋友，教到佢地識backup 為止，唔好俾佢懶啦！<br />\n<br />\n2. 大家最關心既sticker<br />\n其實都有唔少download signal 貼圖既方法，但用呢隻app暫時來講係最方便，<br />\n去Appstore down 'SignalStick' ,隻app 係某巴打寫，可以搵到大部分stickers, 最近收到d push，原來隻app已經有2萬幾套stickers. 重有一個功能係可以轉曬whatsapp d sticker 去signal. 香港人整既app 一定要支持下。<br />\n<br />\nSignalStick iPhone 下載連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/signalstick/id1550231585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fsignalstick%2Fid1550231585&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=5f109818\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/signalstick/id1550231585</a><br />\nAndroid 下載連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.minlabz.stickerhub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.minlabz.stickerhub&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=accbcfd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.minlabz.stickerhub</a><br />\n<br />\n或者入Signal sticker 分享 group<br />\nGroup 2 (上限400人）<br />\n<a href=\"https://signal.group/#CjQKIElAYAEP-aw8WxrW-u5zASn_IHKBFqMZY_Limjb8McBpEhCAjDPl-ZkONzAljKCp00BT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.group%2F%23CjQKIElAYAEP-aw8WxrW-u5zASn_IHKBFqMZY_Limjb8McBpEhCAjDPl-ZkONzAljKCp00BT&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=3aca4195\" target=\"_blank\">https://signal.group/#CjQKIElAYAEP-aw8WxrW-u5zASn_IHKBFqMZY_Limjb8McBpEhCAjDPl-ZkONzAljKCp00BT</a><br />\nGroup 3 (暫未定上限)<br />\n<a href=\"https://signal.group/#CjQKID97bBe7OIFjTGRSdmOkjNy2zxas_bw3jU-XUmVJFZS1EhATdTA6gQO5xVOy7VRHw7qq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.group%2F%23CjQKID97bBe7OIFjTGRSdmOkjNy2zxas_bw3jU-XUmVJFZS1EhATdTA6gQO5xVOy7VRHw7qq&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK9nRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=2e7a77ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://signal.group/#CjQKID97bBe7OIFjTGRSdmOkjNy2zxas_bw3jU-XUmVJFZS1EhATdTA6gQO5xVOy7VRHw7qq</a>"},{"pid":"a9dc53fe0881f6d52ec02d1ffa2f5ed09f5fb9e0","tid":2516095,"uid":344403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"倒數最後10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459e70067db599c90a488c77c558a256a5cf71bb","tid":2516095,"uid":344403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"身邊朋友轉曬Signal未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4855839827a4a4447ffcdfd7e8cb5c5abe79ab22","tid":2516095,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"your name <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5061c8b470f0dc2ea690832e511b8765d7dcd2f0","tid":2516095,"uid":344403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4855839827a4a4447ffcdfd7e8cb5c5abe79ab22","tid":2516095,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T12:15:03.000Z","